+		// PC port: HUD + GUI Interactions render into a 4:3 pillarboxed
+		// design area. UC2 layout was authored against 640x480 (Xbox
+		// native) and mixes pixel-absolute and fraction-of-canvas
+		// conventions; rendering into a fixed 640x480 logical surface
+		// stretched to the pillarbox region resolves both conventions
+		// uniformly without re-authoring assets. Implementation: temporarily
+		// override Canvas->SizeX/Y, ClipX/Y, and Controller->ResX/ResY to
